On Australia's Great
Barrier Reef.

8
00:00:51.802 --> 00:00:53.512
there's a tropical beach

9
00:00:53.887 --> 00:00:56.765
where one tiny turtle's
big adventure

10
00:00:58.183 --> 00:00:59.726
is about to begin.

11
00:01:29.381 --> 00:01:33.969
<i>This is Bun“.</i>

12
00:01:42.853 --> 00:01:45.147
She's a green sea turtle

13
00:01:49.234 --> 00:01:52.112
and today is her birthday.

14
00:01:56.325 --> 00:01:59.161
Out of the hundred eggs she
shared a nest with.

15
00:02:00.203 --> 00:02:03.540
She's the very last
hatchling to emerge.

16
00:02:07.085 --> 00:02:10.422
It will take Bunji a few days to
make it above ground.

17
