00:26:08.108 --> 00:26:10.069
and could easily make a meal

259
00:26:10.235 --> 00:26:12.154
out of a fully grown turtle.

260
00:26:27.127 --> 00:26:29.421
Bunji is in real danger

261
00:26:29.588 --> 00:26:31.507
but she has a plan.

262
00:26:36.345 --> 00:26:38.138
She takes evasive action.

263
00:26:38.305 --> 00:26:41.016
turning her tough shell
towards her attacker.

264
00:26:45.104 --> 00:26:47.356
diving deep to the sea bed.

265
00:26:49.274 --> 00:26:53.320
Down here. she's camouflaged
against the coral.

266
00:26:55.823 --> 00:26:58.117
To limit their time
at the surface.

267
00:26:58.283 --> 00:27:00.327
turtles have evolved the ability

268
00:27:00.494 --> 00:27:03.288
to reduce the amount of
oxygen they need.

269
00:27:06.375 --> 00:27:09.086
They do this by slowing
their heartbeat down

270
00:27:09.253 --> 00:27:12.172
to one beat every minute.

271
00:27:26.061 --> 00:27:28.188
And that means a
green sea turtle

272
00:27:28.355 --> 00:27:31.608
can stay underwater for
over six hours.

273
00:27:57.676 --> 00:28:00.095
But Bunji can't stay
here forever.

274
00:28:01.180 --> 00:28:03.056
As a cold-blooded reptile.

275
00:28:03.223 --> 00:28:08.437
